<chapter id="requirements" xreflabel="Requirements">
<title>Requirements</title>

<para>
The PDB2PQR roll is for use with Rocks &document-version;.
</para>

<para>
You must install the following rolls before installing the PDB2PQR roll:
</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>
python roll is required
</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>
Opal (is required only for web submission).
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

<para>
This roll provides:
</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>
pdb2pqr 1.7.1a
</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>
pdb2pqr 1.8
</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>
ZSI 2.1 a1 
</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>


<para>
You need to install the APBS roll if you want to enable your users to run APBS with PDB2PQR results. 
APBS roll is available from <ulink  url="http://www.poissonboltzmann.org/apbs/downloads">APBS web site</ulink>
</para>

</chapter>
